    </div>
</div>
<div class="jumbotron" id="apps">
    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="col-lg-3">
            <div class="elipse">
                <p><i class="fa fa-windows"></i>&nbsp;<i class="fa fa-android"></i>&nbsp;<i class="fa fa-apple"></i></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-9">
            <h2>I does applications</h2>
            <p>
                I always make websites compatible with mobile phones, but I can also create native apps too.  I have also made
